These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, card-games
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, dancer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, martial-arts
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, mexican
2 different pets are kept: rat, pony
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, bike
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
2. the dancer is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the owner of the rat is the mexican##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | juice     | lemonade       |
| Hobby         | dancing   | card-games     |
| Job           | nurse | dancer   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | horror  |
| Nationality   | mexican | australian |
| Pet           | rat      | pony     |
| Transport     | bike    | car   |

