.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, ambient
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, turkish
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, hamster
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile
1. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the owner of the hamster is the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the turkish is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking milk is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | milk    | sprite |
| Hobby         | sudoku        | traveling  |
| Job           | accountant | dressmaker  |
| Music-Genre   | ambient            | rock    |
| Nationality   | indian     | turkish   |
| Pet           | rabbit         | hamster    |
| Transport     | bus           | snowmobile      |

